messages.messageBody:
Please pass this information on to others.

The Tennhomeschoolers Email list an inclusive list serving Tennhomeschoolers since Feb.
1998. Your hostess - Jacki Willard - networking online with homeschoolers since 1990.
Y'all come visit now, sit a spell, take your shoes off , but be prepared we can be a rowdy
bunch <G> ...

To join:
Send email to: majordomo@...
body: subscribe tennhomeschoolers

for the digest version:
subscribe tennhomeschoolers-digest

Also now forming - Eclectic Homeschoolers of Tennessee
EHT is an inclusive statewide organization serving families across the diverse spectrum of
homeschooling styles and philosophies. EHT has no official political, philosophical, or
religious orientation nor is EHT involved in matters outside of homeschooling.
--
Jacki

There are no strangers here;
Only friends you haven't yet met. W.B. Yeats
